snippet.title: Kimi no Sei (君のせい) Instrumental & Vocaloid Cover [ Seishun Buta Yarou OP ] [ FLP ] [ VSQX ]
snippet.description:
An FL Studio instrumental and vocaloid cover of an anime called Rascal Does Not Dream of Bunny Girl Senpai / Seishun Buta Yarou wa Bunny Girl Senpai no Yume wo Minai (青春ブタ野郎はバニーガール先輩の夢を見ない). 

The original song title is "Kimi no Sei (君のせい)" by the peggies.

here if you want the MP3, FLP or VSQX
MP3 (Instrumental): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1z9E6SPj8LPgtp9WIieWNKA2f82hsbKmB/view?usp=sharing

FLP : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oKWlKMTtfeQjRE3a3-9Ta10D_ohdeb-O/view?usp=sharing
FL Studio version used 12.4. 
I use FL Slayer for the guitar (fast dist, and hardcore for fx)
Boobass for the bass.
fpc for the drums.
and direct wave for the acoustic guitar.

VSQX : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1f_Y4Ts8GNdXVYLfUKNG4-yL92KkdZxrn/view?usp=sharing
Using Vocaloid Editor 4

Thank you for passing by! I hope this will be useful.
